Frequently Asked Questions

  • What is Tubi?
    Tubi is the leading free, premium, on demand video streaming app. We have the largest library of content with over 50,000 movies and television shows, the best streaming technology, and a personalization engine to recommend the best content for you. Available on all of your devices, we give you the best way to discover new content, completely free.
  • Is Tubi really free?
    Yes! Tubi is a free (and legal) video streaming application. To keep our service free and legal, we include ads, which monetize the content that our partners, such as MGM, Lionsgate, and Paramount, provide to us!
